{"tid":369034,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"食左廿幾年雪條 食極都唔完","createTime":"2017-08-22T04:01:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T06:31:54.000Z","uid":22589,"like":11,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"633bafd031c3bceae86568b2f75db8ef572b7fe6","tid":369034,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T04:01:38.000Z","msg":"係我7歲果年買左一枝雪條，從此改變我既一生<br />\n當我奶到最後一啖好失落時，<br />\n枝棍竟然仲多兩條，唔洗講即刻去換黎食<br />\n<br />\n我食完第二枝，吊，又中兩條；<br />\n而第三枝，又仲兩條！結果我再去換四條番黎<br />\n當我食完第五枝後，唔洗講，又中兩條，<br />\n但我已食唔落了，果次係我人生第一次食唔落雪條<br />\n<br />\n我拎番第6~8枝番去比屋企人食，果然每枝再分別各中兩條<br />\n如是者我已經可以再換16條番黎，人生果然充滿希望<br />\n但當我拎番去比屋企人食完後，呢16枝又再各中兩枝，<br />\n我手上渣住16條可兌換32枝既雪條棍，我開始感到到d驚<br />\n<br />\n今次我換完拎番去比同學食，中伏！！<br />\n每枝又獎多兩枝，即係64枝，<br />\n點算？我已幾乎請過晒我識既人食雪條了！<br />\n於是我請埋隔黎班食，但冇喇冇喇，再獎128枝，<br />\n7歲既我，要一次過拎128枝雪條係何其吃力<br />\n<br />\n就咁樣捱左半年，<br />\n我手上仲有20736枝可換41472枝雪條既雪條棍，<br />\n我快要崩潰了！<br />\n難道我餘下既半生都只能活係雪條中嗎！？<br />\n<br />\n轉眼到我24歲果年，<br />\n我已類積左3487459498594498枝一兌二既雪條棍，<br />\n為左搵地方擺雪條，<br />\n我將同女友同居新買既家私全部當晒，<br />\n再用錢去買雪櫃黎裝，<br />\n然後每個月女友一出糧就叫佢比晒錢我買雪櫃去裝，<br />\n但真係冇辦法!!<br />\n我搵錢買雪櫃既速度遠遠追唔上食雪條中雪條既速度!!!!<br />\n<br />\n終於，係我26歲生日果日，女友離我而去，<br />\n佢一句話都冇同我講，<br />\n因為佢個咀已食雪條食到硬化唔講得野。<br />\n我好對佢唔住，<br />\n但人生...我又可以點？<br />\n<br />\n呢年我全個家族因為不停買雪櫃而破產，<br />\n我家族本來係中古時期既貴族後裔，<br />\nd錢洗十世都用唔晒，但竟然落得如廝田地，<br />\n而且我仲有8千幾兆既雪條未換。<br />\n部分擺唔入雪櫃既雪條開始溶化，<br />\nd雪水浸到上我心口，<br />\n我好凍，凍到失去知覺...<br />\n就咁樣一訓，唔知訓左幾多年。"},{"pid":"4f91b5bfbd63f840fe2413f3ea160eb72c1f30e4","tid":369034,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T04:03:05.000Z","msg":"請我食ok?"},{"pid":"db5b1ea219c79a0286edd38104f49210adf44efe","tid":369034,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T04:05:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請我食ok?</blockquote><br />\n唔夠雪櫃融曬了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb27b54538fb48c247728d82f36e0ba9d60017f3","tid":369034,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T04:06:02.000Z","msg":"好似未完"},{"pid":"a15ac7ef740b95f3e294949d3554a51d87b12eca","tid":369034,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T04:06:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>請我食ok?</blockquote><br />\n唔夠雪櫃融曬了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我拎返企自己雪返硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6519e5629de84390388f4ef9375595c2625df2d5","tid":369034,"uid":6242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T04:06:55.000Z","msg":"雀巢公司, 就係你成立"},{"pid":"2fdc1f83e64b0df7644444f076bd0593e7d8a7b7","tid":369034,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T04:08:38.000Z","msg":"邊個叫你咁on9走去兌晒<br />\n想食果陣先拎支棍換唔得既"},{"pid":"c1b008de6669a61f698996c2a013584b009415b9","tid":369034,"uid":55416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T04:11:17.000Z","msg":"賣返啲雪條出去"},{"pid":"b32ab128e628f7900d5f1b465c07d21e999727b0","tid":369034,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T04:11:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>請我食ok?</blockquote><br />\n唔夠雪櫃融曬了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我拎返企自己雪返硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n水黎架wo 你屋企都有啦"},{"pid":"8ad17daaf0d00e0c95b3fe82b5b15796b217b47e","tid":369034,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T04:12:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>請我食ok?</blockquote><br />\n唔夠雪櫃融曬了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我拎返企自己雪返硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n水黎架wo 你屋企都有啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b223f124e1a97c4ac1aece74e22f1ab79aeb355c","tid":369034,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T04:12:34.000Z","msg":"樓主食咩宵夜"},{"pid":"39bc9a418451845e0f53ea8e073a59763a8ed14b","tid":369034,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T04:13:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雀巢公司, 就係你成立</blockquote><br />\n唔係 <br />\n我醒番時掰大眼見到個呀伯，佢話有辦法幫我，<br />\n我問點樣，佢就話只要將我手上既雪條棍賣晒比佢，<br />\n佢就會開一間雪條公司賣雪條，<br />\n等人買左後再拎雪條棍黎換，<br />\n<br />\n比如10個人買左10條，<br />\n走番黎獎20條，佢就前後清左30條；<br />\n果廿條再獎四十條，佢再比，又清多八十條...<br />\n如是者向全世界輻射出去，最終就會解脫到<br />\n<br />\n我恍然大悟，一路多謝佢一路&rarr;即走，<br />\n走左成百米遠後我回頭問佢係咩人，<br />\n佢答我係瑞士人，叫亨利內斯特萊。"},{"pid":"43eec5e4976135b4dd724970dc7b8f227e26de21","tid":369034,"uid":35152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T04:13:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>請我食ok?</blockquote><br />\n唔夠雪櫃融曬了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我拎返企自己雪返硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n水黎架wo 你屋企都有啦</blockquote><br />\n啲水都比你笠晒了"},{"pid":"f088f09c458f1f474cc76c97b2ba3f4d63a316c8","tid":369034,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T04:14:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>請我食ok?</blockquote><br />\n唔夠雪櫃融曬了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我拎返企自己雪返硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n水黎架wo 你屋企都有啦</blockquote><br />\n啲水都比你笠晒了</blockquote><br />\n係<br />\n遲下粒埋伯友啲西水"},{"pid":"0ca07703d2c80f22cb4148fb0fce2bfd88b917e0","tid":369034,"uid":117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T04:15:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>雀巢公司, 就係你成立</blockquote><br />\n唔係 <br />\n我醒番時掰大眼見到個呀伯，佢話有辦法幫我，<br />\n我問點樣，佢就話只要將我手上既雪條棍賣晒比佢，<br />\n佢就會開一間雪條公司賣雪條，<br />\n等人買左後再拎雪條棍黎換，<br />\n<br />\n比如10個人買左10條，<br />\n走番黎獎20條，佢就前後清左30條；<br />\n果廿條再獎四十條，佢再比，又清多八十條...<br />\n如是者向全世界輻射出去，最終就會解脫到<br />\n<br />\n我恍然大悟，一路多謝佢一路&rarr;即走，<br />\n走左成百米遠後我回頭問佢係咩人，<br />\n佢答我係瑞士人，叫亨利內斯特萊。</blockquote><br />\n只會係一開始買果幾個不斷loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a36cccc90052c4f1e1005d6210513c1fb6caf3d","tid":369034,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T04:16:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主食咩宵夜</blockquote><br />\n咁撚熱要食狗肉 配雪條一流"},{"pid":"db4e5306e3f86386b16453707884025a51ee99f6","tid":369034,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T04:48:38.000Z","msg":"請我食ok?唔想執二手飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad089e4f4d90dceefb99643657e49dfc314700f1","tid":369034,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T05:02:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請我食ok?唔想執二手飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n賣曬比個阿伯了"},{"pid":"21c4a4690db638ad060b884e9e1e34ad0a0e58db","tid":369034,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T05:37:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>請我食ok?唔想執二手飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n賣曬比個阿伯了</blockquote><br />\n鳩白？？"},{"pid":"9f9c211135f9aebfaa8fc778f6e888937f8aa6e2","tid":369034,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T05:38:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>請我食ok?唔想執二手飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n賣曬比個阿伯了</blockquote><br />\n鳩白？？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b9cc799792d3b27dced2639f7fb34c1c85ad91","tid":369034,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T05:38:42.000Z","msg":"比幾條我oj?"},{"pid":"7a272f8c93c87998ff1f48c88b360b1be281e9b9","tid":369034,"uid":82155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T05:39:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />老是常出現"},{"pid":"68f4ad21b154cdba0717138641ae94e9a2800d3d","tid":369034,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T05:39:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比幾條我oj?</blockquote><br />\n聽日食完飯過黎比你"},{"pid":"db3f7d462a60f2965d8499ec2f33e080d89afe84","tid":369034,"uid":72946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T05:40:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>雀巢公司, 就係你成立</blockquote><br />\n唔係 <br />\n我醒番時掰大眼見到個呀伯，佢話有辦法幫我，<br />\n我問點樣，佢就話只要將我手上既雪條棍賣晒比佢，<br />\n佢就會開一間雪條公司賣雪條，<br />\n等人買左後再拎雪條棍黎換，<br />\n<br />\n比如10個人買左10條，<br />\n走番黎獎20條，佢就前後清左30條；<br />\n果廿條再獎四十條，佢再比，又清多八十條...<br />\n如是者向全世界輻射出去，最終就會解脫到<br />\n<br />\n我恍然大悟，一路多謝佢一路&rarr;即走，<br />\n走左成百米遠後我回頭問佢係咩人，<br />\n佢答我係瑞士人，叫世界情色王。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"ea5930a00d36136b584705577d09a793b19893ce","tid":369034,"uid":47966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T05:47:32.000Z","msg":"雀巢潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}